    description: "Zenodo archive (v0.1.0)"
abstract: >-
  A contamination-resistant synthetic benchmark for agentic-RAG / memory systems.
  Five metrics (conversion, chain-fragility, distraction, fact-retention-at-budget,
  outcome-ranked recall) with pre-registered falsifiers, bootstrap confidence
  intervals, a frozen sha256-pinned dataset, a single runner, and a
  number-verification ledger.
